This is the fully HDR compatible version of gg_vacant.
So if your pc cant run HDR or your afraid of lags because of it dl the normal version.
--------------------------------------------------------------
http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/61480

***Updated*** 1.1
Following features where added:
Bot Nav_file
Radar overview 
Darker Light
Volumetric Fog
A text intro in the class selection menu


gg_vacant is a remake of a CoD 4 map called Vacant.
It has 32 player support and is about 90% accurate to the real one.

Mods also compatible:
Team-Deathmatch
